sentences: Ayako Fuji (藤あや子, Fuji Ayako) (real name Manami Fujimura (藤村真奈美, Fujimura Manami), née Takahashi (高橋)), born May 10, 1961, is a Japanese enka singer.
Born in Kakunodate, Akita, Fuji graduated from Akita Prefectural Kakunodate South High School.
Fuji made her enka debut on September 21, 1989.
